        <item>
            <title>1.3.0</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 09:34:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>202606150933</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.3.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## What's Changed
* feat(update): disable real updates in make run dev builds by @BlackHole1 in https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/pull/12
* feat(log): differentiate activation reasons and add row context by @BlackHole1 in https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/pull/13
* feat(url): support Firefox-based browsers in per-URL rules by @BlackHole1 in https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/pull/14
* feat(build): separate dev app identity from releases by @BlackHole1 in https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/pull/15
* fix(update): derive stop identity from lab run copy by @BlackHole1 in https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/pull/16
* feat(backup): add config export/import via .lockime files by @BlackHole1 in https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/pull/18
* build(dmg): shrink download by trimming icon slot and using ULFO by @BlackHole1 in https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/pull/19
* refactor(update): render release notes natively, dropping MarkdownUI by @BlackHole1 in https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/pull/21
* feat(rules): add one-shot switch action for app/URL rules by @BlackHole1 in https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/pull/22


* docs(test): note the expected CoreData stderr in the fallback test ([`e9834e8`](https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/commit/e9834e874fd3adb9f480c95080033d202ba88c58))

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/compare/v1.2.2...v1.3.0
]]></description>
